Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:05.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:36.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:40.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:09.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:11.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:18.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not deep enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's face…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was Inoue's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:21.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Inoue's brother\Ncome after me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But judging from the Hollow that\Nattacked you last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it seems a powerful Hollow\Nwho remains in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,wants to devour\Nyour spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it probably controls\Nseveral Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then Inoue's brother's appearance\Nwould make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way! So, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't kill Inoue's brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:52.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think! If you don't kill him,\Nhe will wander around forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no doubt that\Nhe will attack you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we may not have time\Nto worry about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How about\Nsome dessert now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have some leeks and\Nbean jam jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:15.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They go great together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too keen for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…poor Enraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible.\NHow come you're all torn up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:30.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollows target their own kin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It happens frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows are fallen souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Souls that were not guided into\Nthe Soul Society by a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:56.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Souls that were not protected\Nby Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They lose their hearts and\Nbecome Hollows themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that this Hollow has\Nfailed to devour you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he will go after the soul of\Nthe one he loved most in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the bruise\Non Inoue's leg today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was the mark left by a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:23.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then that accident was\NInoue's brother's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!\NHow come there's blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that ghostly thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this chain?\NI can't breathe…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here in a daze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki! Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:16.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:31.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She can't hear us,\Nlet alone see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How…How do you\Nknow my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How sad, Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:48.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten my voice?\NIt's me…can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:54.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How sad…\NI'm so sad! So sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:05.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I the one you're after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Tatsuki, you got\Ncaught up in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:28.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It IS you! But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue… Say, how come\Nyou can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh… Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers are spiritual beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only other spiritual beings can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for\Nordinary people to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual being…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:18.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Ichigo! Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go!\NKurosaki is hurt! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Wake up, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:12.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to talk?\NWhere were you hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:22.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He may have been Inoue's\Nolder brother, but he's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:27.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a human heart.\NKill him without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying. My brother would\Nnever do what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were forgetting\Nabout me…little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:58.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After I died,\Nyou prayed for me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I watched you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:06.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was your prayers\Nthat gave me peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:14.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But after about a year,\Nyou became friends with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you began praying for me\Nless and less often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:28.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And when you entered high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you stopped praying for me altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why…I was so lonely…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you're wrong…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:45.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have even a shred\Nof feeling left for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,do not betray me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour that Soul Reaper\Nand end this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Kurosaki has\Nnothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Brother!\NDon't hurt him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think it is\Nthat I became this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:15.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will listen to what I say!\NOtherwise…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why big brothers\Nare born first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:54.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's to protect the little brothers\Nand sisters that follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:55.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you're threatening to\Nkill your own sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that,\Neven if you are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Orihime is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:11.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I raised her when our parents\Nabandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was when Orihime was three…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:18.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've protected her ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:29.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me! If you listen to me,\NI won't lay a hand on the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:31.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:36.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He no longer has\Nthe feelings of a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:33.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime is…mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:41.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if! Inoue is Inoue!\NShe doesn't belong…to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating!\NFinish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ori…hime…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:41.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault. It's all because\NI begged you not to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:48.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Please don't die!\NPlease don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:56.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you couldn't…rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:05.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed that you were\Nalways beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even yesterday,\Nwhen that car almost hit me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You pulled my leg to\Nget me out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:25.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if I keep depending on you,\Nyou'll never be able to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to show you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.\NYou don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that made you lonely…and sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:56.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting the Hollow inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't become\Na Hollow by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He probably was taken over\Nby a Hollow.…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:04.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His target was supposed\Nto be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A soul that is devoured by\Na strong Hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is manipulated by that Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a Hollow who is\Nafter you took over a soul
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,whom you would hesitate to fight,\Nand forced him to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:27.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he is desperately\Nfighting that Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For his sister's sake…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ori…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:44.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The chain attached to her chest,\Nthe Chain of Fate, is still connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it is connected,\Nshe will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I need to treat her. Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can use my Kido to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You gave that to her\Nas a present, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue said so…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she wears\Nit every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:33.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I stay here like this,\Neventually I'll revert to being a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:43.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So now…while I still have\Na semblance of sanity…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey wait…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's making the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you become a Hollow,\Nyou can never go back to what you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let him pass on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:04.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Reaping a Hollow\Nis not really killing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're cleansing its soul and\Nallowing it to enter the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we\NSoul Reapers exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:38.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This hairpin that you\Nbought me that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We had a fight over it, remember?\NBecause I said it was too childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I let you go to work\Nwithout saying anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last time\N I would see you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:59.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, I want to say it now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A sumo champion\Nreally came to my room…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and blasted a hole with a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:03.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not again! Can't you make\Nit sound more realistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At least, say a pro wrestler came\Nand caused a brawl outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like Hime's silly imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it's true! Right, Tatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:20.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tatsuki, don't tell me you agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So is that what you did yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, what is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:33.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Memory Replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I erased her memories of tonight\Nand replaced them with new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Memory Replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:46.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't choose the new memories,\Nwhich can be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nwe'll find out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You used it on my family\Nthe other day, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:58.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the resolve\Nto do this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not such a fine human being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that I can promise to risk\Nmy life for a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:11.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:19.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a total slime who'd watch\Nsomeone get hurt before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you…\Ndo the work of a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:04.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:08.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:14.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:19.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:23.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:33.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:44.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, thank you for watching\Nover me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:46.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…Brother, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:53.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…This is supposed to be the preview…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:54.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw no, we're out of time again!